<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/main.css">
    <script src="scripts/marquee.js"></script>
    <title>Document</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    {% include "./partials/header.njk" %}
    <main>
      <section class="bg-site-bg overflow-hidden">
        <h2 class="text-xl  w-full text-left md:text-center md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold py-8">Discover trending coins</h2>
        <p class="hidden md:block text-center w-2/5 m-auto mb-10">We offer a wide range of coins you can buy on our site. Below
          are some of the ones that have received the most attention from our customers.</p>
        <div class="container mx-auto flex py-10">
          {% for data in tickerData -%}
            <div class="flex flex-wrap min-w-1/4 bg-white text-gray-800 p-5 rounded-2xl shadow-card ml-5">
              <div class="flex w-full justify-between items-center">
                <div class="flex content-center">
                  <img src="{{ data.image }}" class="w-7"/>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-bold ml-3">{{ data.name }}</h3>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase">{{ data.symbol }}</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="w-full font-bold text-3xl pt-6">â‚¬{{ data.current_price | round }}</p>
              <p class="w-full text-sm">+{{ data.price_change_percentage_24h | round(2) }}% in the past 24 hours</p>
            </div>
          {%- endfor %}
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="bg-site-secondary-bg">
        <div class="whyarlan bg-site-secondary-bg container mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-xl text-left md:text-center md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold py-8">Why choose Arlan?</h2>
          <p class="hidden md:block text-center w-2/5 m-auto mb-10">We believe that every person, no matter their experience or
            skills should be able to purchase cryptocurrencies. That's why we use a simple system, to make it as easy as possible,
            yet still secure and competitive with the rest.</p>
          <div class="discover__list flex flex-wrap m-auto md:justify-between">
            <div class="discover__list--item bg-white my-4 mb-12 rounded-xl shadow-card">
              <div class="list__item--content p-4">
                <img src="media/whyarlan/safe.png" class="m-auto -mt-12"/>
                <h3 class="font-bold pb-4 text-2xl">Safe</h3>
                <p>With countell checks and the latest technologies, your transactions are secured on multiple levels.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="discover__list--item bg-white my-4 mb-12 rounded-xl shadow-card">
              <div class="list__item--content p-4">
                <img src="media/whyarlan/simple.png" class="m-auto -mt-12"/>
                <h3 class="font-bold pb-4 text-2xl">Simple</h3>
                <p>We strive to make out platform easy to use, so anybody can get involved in investing and start making money from it.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="discover__list--item bg-white my-4  mb-12 rounded-xl shadow-card">
              <div class="list__item--content p-4">
                <img src="media/whyarlan/competitive.png" class="m-auto -mt-12"/>
                <h3 class="font-bold pb-4 text-2xl">Competitive</h3>
                <p>Because we're able to sell packets of coins, we are able to sell at a very competitive price compared to other
                  platforms.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      {% include "./partials/cryptocurrencies.njk" %}</body>
  </body>
</html></main>{% include "./partials/footer.njk" %}<script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/eefbba8f9b.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
<script src="scripts/app.js"></script>
</html></body></html>